Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是破忌者追击部队 卡拉德小队副队长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}还未填满绝望的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克·斯塔卡德中士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉席恩·阿斯塔尔陛下之命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前来处分你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有求于你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如陛下之命 请你杀了莱纳·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影 现形
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你那肮脏的手碰蜜尔可·卡拉德一根头发试试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立马杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝不饶恕伤害亲人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你明白了 就眨一下眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我就放了蜜尔可·卡拉德吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认她平安无事之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的命掌握在我手中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是慎重小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是勇者遗物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是捡了莱纳·琉特忘记回收的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根针上可以延伸出无限的丝线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且强韧得无法可断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到使用者的力量能使其变成如此危险的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若罗兰德以外的国家掌握了它…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说加斯塔克吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你应该看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直监视他的旅途 你有什么想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳·琉特对罗兰德 对席恩·阿斯塔尔陛下来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是必须的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人死亡 没有人哭泣的和平世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精彩 这理想真是太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而这不过…是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直隐藏了实力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你离开陛下 也无视寻你归国的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡去了国外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要遵守命令杀了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是很善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜尔可队长会喜欢上你 也很容易理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死会令队长伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 这是我个人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人 不应该留在陛下身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫拉 拉夫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负基本已定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 无论如何反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都赢不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两侧有陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看破了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太过自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算继续活下去…我这种人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？原来你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 我杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？原来你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想干…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？原来你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我道歉 脚下留情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请你吃团子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 为什么那个人要杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟踪我来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…我来挡住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:07:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么不像平时一样 吃掉周围的人治愈伤口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你搞不好真会被我干掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳 请您…履行约定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复写眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖取结晶 「噬石」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先来两个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也赶快发狂变成结晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对人类感到绝望 悲哀的神之眼持有者们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你来拯救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你善良 脆弱 害怕寂寞到令人感到悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 不是一般的快啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来几次都是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混账！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太碍事了 歼灭眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求烧原 红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:09:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 啊可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结晶化之前就杀掉了可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你白痴啊 竟然在放魔法途中插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴的是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…那么想一个人去死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是怪物 不是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就随你消失好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是觉得不是我的搭档或下仆 也不是喝茶的伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就随你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我不这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你多么坚信自己是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你独自一人也不感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也无法这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真是让我看了场好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是童话什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后怪物就会变成人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可贺可喜可贺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不巧那家伙是怪物这事实是雷打不动的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是怪物还是什么 我都不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说话真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他是活着即是祸害的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在乎世界可在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险的怪物不能留活路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我管他那么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他那么多…你这什么话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太随便了…这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以活下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你要是死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会很寂寞呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你马上就要感到寂寞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他就要死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共鸣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时…一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 住口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏所有 消灭一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生 死 喜 悲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 住口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要挣扎 这就是你的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论世界如何充满绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快结束这一切吧 如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放 打开 杀戮 一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到眼前的一切尽数消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到眼前的一切尽数消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会伤害人的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这双血染的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法触碰任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我依然想拯救 想触及
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这双手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还能有所作为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…混账！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止了…结晶化？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉杰尔之线？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这玩意叫这个名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我把你的头颅送去加斯塔克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟罗兰德找茬有什么下场…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们好好见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「噬石」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鸣 电光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里我来挡住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去救孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的归处 不是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉唉 搞什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果收获只有一个结晶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开所有公式者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到已经出现在罗兰德了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有…公式？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己的事都不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是滑稽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说勇者还没完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来情况发生了很大变化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝小姐应该快醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是轻微脑震荡 不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你真的…不是普通怪物的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你走后 你可知道他是什么表情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为 他是真的想杀了你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:18:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自己背负一切 努力撑到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的王 和你们的王不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是真心想创造一个人人欢笑度日的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个不折不扣的大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己放下大话还这样 我还真是无可救药
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过你无可救药也不是现在才开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过我觉得你们也够笨的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地来追我这个无可救药的窝囊废
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为害怕受伤 害怕伤人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才逃了出来 孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 实际上根本无法孤单下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论以为自己多么绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀的是 心却还…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:18:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回罗兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我的力量还有用武之地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克也有危险的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 我有一件事要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果下次我再发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直逃避自己是个怪物的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直害怕自己会杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 希望你给我勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇气？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我不再逃避 奋战至最后的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样你就会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:20:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳·琉特似乎主动回归了罗兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 大陆各地相当数量的魔眼持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在集结反加斯塔克势力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以莱纳·琉特为桥梁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结成反加斯塔克战线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是今后值得考虑的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西没有任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论莱纳能派上什么用场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者多么无能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本要是卢克·斯塔卡德能杀了莱纳·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样对你来说反而更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会下那种命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会杀莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会杀莱纳·琉特？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你是要选择最残酷的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说莱纳或许是重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为早点杀掉会比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他 马上会有代替品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同为世界的齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么也不必牺牲朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只需走上正确的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必要的话 甚至能牺牲所有重要之人的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 爱人也都能牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你唯一的资质
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不要后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:04.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}忘れてたあの日の面影が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:04.41,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}那一天已忘却的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:10.37,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}空の向こう 微かに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:10.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}在天空彼方隐隐浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:18.45,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}心なら繋がっていたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:18.45,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}心灵原本应早已相通
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:25.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}震えた瞳は応えずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:25.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}颤抖的瞳眸却无回应
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:29.21,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}どんなに信じても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:29.21,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}如何相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:32.66,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}どんなに伝えたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:32.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}如何呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:38.96,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}この声は届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:38.96,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}这声音你已无法听到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:43.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}光のフィルメント
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:43.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}光之Fillment
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:48.61,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}全てをこの身体に刻み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:48.61,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}一一铭刻于此身
